  "texts": [
    "Given these concerns, a thorough and rigorous assessment of LLMs' responsible and effective use in healthcare is essential.",
    "The following section will further examine the workings of LLMs, and their potential mental health applications, and critically evaluate the opportunities and challenges they introduce.",
    "LLMs represent significant advancements in machine learning (ML), characterized by their ability to understand and generate human-like text with high accuracy.",
    "Distinguished from traditional language models by their scale, LLMs often contain billions of parameters 18.",
    "This LLMs are designed to learn the fundamental statistical patterns of language 21."
  ]
}